headline: Primis and Absolute Sports Announce Partnership to Deliver Video Discovery Across Their Global Portfolio of Websites
summary: Primis, the video discovery platform for publishers and part of the McCann and IPG network (NYSE: IPG), has signed an exclusive partnership with Absolute Sports, the global digital media group behind Sportskeeda.com, and other leading brands. With over 80 million monthly users and reach across 150+ countries, Absolute Sports is a leading force in global digital sports media.
